content: **Photorealistic painting of a very pretty young Korean woman wearing office clothes in an office and looking at me with a broad smile, Cinematic and hyper-detailed, this painting depicts a young Korean woman in her office attire, her beauty stunningly captured in the insane details that make up her features. Beautifully color graded with Unreal Engine technology, the depth of field (DOF) effect highlights her perfectly rendered face, while the super-resolution and megapixel count ensure that every detail is hyper-realistic. The cinematic lighting, anti-aliasing, FKAA, TXAA, RTX, SSAO, and post-processing techniques used in the creation of this masterpiece bring it to life with unparalleled realism. The post-production process involved precise tone mapping, CGI, VFX, and SFX to create an insanely detailed and intricate painting that is hyper-maximalist in its approach. Volumetric and photorealistic, every inch of this artwork is ultra-detailed, with intricate details that are visible even in 8K resolution. The super-detailed and full-color painting is brought to life with volumetric lighting and HDR, adding to the realism of the scene. The use of Unreal Engine and 16K resolution ensures that every aspect of the painting is in sharp focus, with each individual element contributing to the overall stunning effect. This painting is not just photorealistic, but ultra photoreal, capturing the beauty of the young Korean woman in a way that is breathtakingly real.** - Upscaled by <@480277223484424203> (fast)
